{"tid":1381588,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【公務員站出來】一群公務員致公會的公開信","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T07:58:55.000Z","uid":20820,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fb32d121ba9d350ced1ebf3d824c209678613517","tid":1381588,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:23:58.000Z","msg":"【公務員站出來】<br />\n<br />\n致香港文書職系公務員總會<br />\n<br />\n    近兩個月來，香港人如何處於水深火熱的境地，是有目共睹的。自白衣人襲擊元朗港鐵站後，市民對警察的信任更是跌至前所未有的低谷。然而，無論社會上對警方之惡劣行徑如何口誅筆伐，皆無法阻止警方不公的執法，警方的行動甚至有變本加厲之象。<br />\n  <br />\n    上星期，數十部門、過千位同事已分別發岀聲明，道出各同事的心聲，表達出我們的痛心。而政務司司長亦於訪問時提到，認為現時警方做法有問題。作為公務員的一份子，我們不能再等待，故懇請總會牽頭，帶領全體公務員響應民間即將舉行的全民集會、遊行，甚至是罷工。<br />\n<br />\n    我們不是要總會與警為敵，而是要與民同行。希望總會能起牽頭作用，召集各位有心的公務員出來。我們目的只有一個，令政府真正回應市民的訴求，不要再讓施政錯誤，警察濫權、使用過份武力的情況持續惡化下去！<br />\n<br />\n我們清楚知道公務員的守則上列出公務員需要政治中立，然而<br />\n政治中立，不等於不能發聲<br />\n政治中立，不等於埋沒良知<br />\n政治中立，不等於顛倒是非<br />\n政治中立，不等於盲目支持施政<br />\n<br />\n    當社會各界，包括港鐵車長也紛紛作出聯署的時候，作為人民公僕的我們又豈能離棄市民？我們必需與民同行！我們已準備好，請總會帶領香港公務員，於星期五到中環集會，與民同行，為民發聲。<br />\n<br />\n      我們一向尊重總會為我們走的每一步，現在正是時候為公務員，為香港人走出這一步，讓政府真正回應民間五大訴求。你願意帶領，我們願意站出來！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n一群真心為港的公務員上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hVwNU9Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhVwNU9Y.png&h=7de24c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（借朋友acc出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"a13901dc958bfeff860c58101cad0ddbeac3f4fb","tid":1381588,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"支持2/8集會！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［重開 長文慎屌］727 728 賽後檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2df21f0509e34e324f5945692946b6dd266ed191","tid":1381588,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係我地既英雄"},{"pid":"d19370211d4dabd1e139a7294c92327897f7c056","tid":1381588,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:25:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac82461a34e2c43051afbb0274408fe2b0bf98cd","tid":1381588,"uid":229019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMV3tnr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMV3tnr.png&h=77fc1786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Rgez2q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Rgez2q.png&h=b86a56fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgkSmHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgkSmHq.jpg&h=d447c2f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KY6Vjt5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKY6Vjt5.jpg&h=18989aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLe7U2r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLe7U2r.jpg&h=98c959ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eba993aa45805f743ddd7d63c4810dbf6d3e9c2","tid":1381588,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4c38a116834952b163ee974dd11b37a3a57ebe","tid":1381588,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741abc40e06fcf786dde984fcd9d24774c0a3293","tid":1381588,"uid":61035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1ebf89e32a96ccd29ab2a53d3cbb30fc2873fbae","tid":1381588,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislik